{"tid":25490,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚醫生！！ 扁桃腺炎","createTime":"2016-12-06T07:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T17:27:07.000Z","uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3480aac6db6248b2424f7c6d25b67369bb5f7f9b","tid":25490,"uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:00:45.000Z","msg":"之前已經連續左大半年 一個月一次扁桃腺炎<br />\n次次都會病得好嚴重 發燒周身骨痛 醫生話次次都係急性黎<br />\n<br />\n所以我都習慣左一發現有小小唔舒服就照一照喉嚨<br />\n頭先照左一照 又發現有一點好細既白點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n有冇方法可以即刻做啲咩 食啲咩會好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  黎緊好多日都好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b8706221f2997e671aaa1eb91de05404a28680","tid":25490,"uid":2111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:06:02.000Z","msg":"呢個病慘過死"},{"pid":"571ffc82f1248188562295239dbc44d73bc63aa0","tid":25490,"uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:07:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個病慘過死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752fa890bce61b12df3797b49a1686ccaab7a68a","tid":25490,"uid":8716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:12:35.000Z","msg":"每三個幾月發一次 開頭第一二次都仲會發燒 慢慢就淨係喉嚨唔舒服 每次都起哂白點腫哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一發炎就好鐘意用電話開閃光燈照黎睇"},{"pid":"8ff59bf0beb2595c60264481fb1946e99d619c00","tid":25490,"uid":37054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:17:11.000Z","msg":"通常瘋狂飲水 沖哂d白色野落肚<br />\nD白色野r出黎聞臭過屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d63612314166e3f765ef1c9f2366250357ecf517","tid":25490,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:17:55.000Z","msg":"我個兩粒好大舊<br />\n日日搵電筒照 挑d白色珍珠出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但身體冇咩病痛"},{"pid":"7ef23b7d2ecef69ce865258566fde1ab03b22c7f","tid":25490,"uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:22:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常瘋狂飲水 沖哂d白色野落肚<br />\nD白色野r出黎聞臭過屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經狂啪水 同龍角散 我果啲唔係結石黎 係濃黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e1483d85d1ca7a2e0f92384b0102ab3fb27788","tid":25490,"uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:23:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每三個幾月發一次 開頭第一二次都仲會發燒 慢慢就淨係喉嚨唔舒服 每次都起哂白點腫哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一發炎就好鐘意用電話開閃光燈照黎睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我今年已經第7次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468928ae34ffc8c005fde06362eee6c4bf800311","tid":25490,"uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:56:06.000Z","msg":"岩岩沖走左啲白色濃 希望好得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d148e8b861e75d08105ca012754d3bd2839737","tid":25490,"uid":37267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:04:24.000Z","msg":"你咁樣可以切左佢"},{"pid":"8bdc312c1c0b50051a565703d43540fa7ed3ea61","tid":25490,"uid":24033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:07:53.000Z","msg":"免疫系統有事？"},{"pid":"363f8b71fcd6d29bb0fa27dcb4330708e442a4e9","tid":25490,"uid":7416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:20:35.000Z","msg":"好在自己唔係成日咁 我淨係試過一兩次 都已經辛苦到想死 呑唔到口水 講唔到野 勁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主 好似可以割架如果你係經常性發炎既話 問下醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a2cff15de2586c006779e7be15ab4e3a215409","tid":25490,"uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咁樣可以切左佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n醫生話可以唔切 叫我早啲訓 做多啲運動增多抵抗力。<br />\n<br />\n始終都好煩 要約時間做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467e788ba0d27072e2adf5c4b896d8fe12eb3370","tid":25490,"uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:22:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>免疫系統有事？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n醫生話我抵抗力差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係我未連續扁桃腺炎之前一直都好小病"},{"pid":"24cf387d77ece1d3e099dd467139297f43edb1fd","tid":25490,"uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:24:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好在自己唔係成日咁 我淨係試過一兩次 都已經辛苦到想死 呑唔到口水 講唔到野 勁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主 好似可以割架如果你係經常性發炎既話 問下醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n始終切左可以一了百了，過埋新年都再病先去切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a4ffcbe493696441d0ee4a6d15eb57734c150f","tid":25490,"uid":51418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:24:59.000Z","msg":"咁岩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係，呑口水都痛到仆街"},{"pid":"4997913184b1a867eea129250d222eb69ea9c211","tid":25490,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:25:33.000Z","msg":"之前又係一個月發一次，跟住忍唔住去咗做手術<br />\n做完第二日傷口爆開狂嘔血，又再入醫院再做，仲訓咗3日先出得返嚟<br />\n兩星期先食到固體野<br />\n<br />\n比我再揀真係唔會做，又痛又食唔到野又講唔到野，好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b731bc3833257faa47feb090321beb333593e6dc","tid":25490,"uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:26:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁岩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係，呑口水都痛到仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我發燒頭病比較嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好影響工作表現"},{"pid":"389047615846f0344ceb76a91afe7666112d5a47","tid":25490,"uid":29879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:27:32.000Z","msg":"yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我又係成日咁，醫生話我天生個扁bo"},{"pid":"abbcdc50a7fd365d60766afece2214b31329de25","tid":25490,"uid":51418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:27:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁岩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係，呑口水都痛到仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我發燒頭病比較嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好影響工作表現</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都燒左幾日，燒到40度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 星期六到依家都冇返工"},{"pid":"4e1bbc4386bd63b072f03c3d578f0a60e09babdd","tid":25490,"uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:29:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前又係一個月發一次，跟住忍唔住去咗做手術<br />\n做完第二日傷口爆開狂嘔血，又再入醫院再做，仲訓咗3日先出得返嚟<br />\n兩星期先食到固體野<br />\n<br />\n比我再揀真係唔會做，又痛又食唔到野又講唔到野，好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSo9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真？ 但係我一直都斷唔到尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f67012b1795ef34fa7a079ff7867e7f0414d294","tid":25490,"uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:31:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我又係成日咁，醫生話我天生個扁bo</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來咁多同病相連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我試過有一次腫到左右兩邊合埋左 ， 就算依家好返 都比之前腫"},{"pid":"5ff595fc45e817c56925a620d9db027f32fc68a2","tid":25490,"uid":29879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:31:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我又係成日咁，醫生話我天生個扁bo</blockquote><br />\n醫生話我天生個扁桃腺大過人，好易收埋d菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n輕則吞口水痛<br />\n重則就發燒咳鼻水喉一次過黎曬<br />\n仲要好難先好番，食成個星期坑生素都好唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf02afca9262703f6101358856345ee7862b119","tid":25490,"uid":29879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:35:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁岩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係，呑口水都痛到仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我發燒頭病比較嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好影響工作表現</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都燒左幾日，燒到40度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 星期六到依家都冇返工</blockquote><br />\n我上個月又係咁 燒左4日先退燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又係燒到40度之後係咁退燒又番發又退燒又番發咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144c9db747507817996e971642a703e79f25c803","tid":25490,"uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:35:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我又係成日咁，醫生話我天生個扁bo</blockquote><br />\n醫生話我天生個扁桃腺大過人，好易收埋d菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n輕則吞口水痛<br />\n重則就發燒咳鼻水喉一次過黎曬<br />\n仲要好難先好番，食成個星期坑生素都好唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀。真係食成個星期都好唔返 醫生話可能有抗藥性 跟住要轉第二隻食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我果時係要keep住係咁食退燒藥 驚返返下工又發燒"}]}